{"word":"ἀκήριος 2","slug":"ἀκήριος 2","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n3153\" key=\"a)kh/rios2\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀκήριος</orth> (B), <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">κῆρ</etym>) <sense id=\"n3153.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">without heart</tr_>, i.e., </sense> <sense n=\"I\" id=\"n3153.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">lifeless</tr_>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> (not in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> </bibl>), <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀκήριον αἶψα τίθησι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:392\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.392</biblScope></bibl></cit>. cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:466\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.466</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n3153.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">heartless, spiritless</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σέ που δέος ἴσχει ἀκήριον</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:812\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.812</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:224\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.224</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἥμενοι αὖθι ἕκαστοι ἀκήριοι</q